                   fi.protie.navigation Changelog
                   ------------------------------
Legend:
- All items marked with "!" represent a major API-Change that is
  not guaranteed to be backwards compatible to previous versions
  which might even break existing functionality.
- All items marked with "+" represent completely new features.

2008-01-09 adrenalin
  - Added configurable option for inserting the class name to the link tag as well.

2007-11-23 adrenalin
  ! Corrected mispelled 'childs' to 'children', which might force someone to change the
    CSS class names

2007-06-12 adrenalin
  - Added (again) 'untranslated' to class name for multilang

2007-05-23 adrenalin
  - Fixed someone's buggy implementation of setting the ID of the root ul element

2006-12-13 adrenalin
  - Added the files `csshover.htc` and `dropdown.css` to support CSS
    dropdown menus

2006-11-03 adrenalin
  - First changelog entry
  + Added support for restricting navigation to a certain amount of levels

